<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Death Ponee</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Boogaloo&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0a0a0a, #1a1a1a);
        color: #ffcf00;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem 1rem;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
      }

        section {
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
      }

        #home {
        padding-bottom: 6rem;
      }

        #about {
        padding-top: 5rem;
      }
        #about p {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

        #about h2 {
        color: #ffcf00;
      }


      h1 {
        font-family: 'Boogaloo', sans-serif;
        font-size: 5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #ffcf00;
      }

      h2 {
        font-weight: normal;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #ffcf00;
      }

      .album-covers {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }

      .album-covers img {
        max-width: 300px;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #000;
      }

      .links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .links a {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #252525;
        color: #ffcf00;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 1px solid #ffcf00;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .links a:hover {
        background-color: #ffcf00;
        color: #000;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .album-covers img {
         max-width: 45%;
      }
}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="home">
      <h1>Death Ponee</h1>
      <h2>New album: <em>Waiting for Rover</em> – out now</h2>

      <div class="album-covers">
        <img src="/Final Front copy_for Digital (2).jpg" alt="Album cover front" />
        <img src="/Final Back copy_for Digital.jpg" alt="Album cover back" />
      </div>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://open.spotify.com/album/7DLH0CwDNEX6SX8OLLb3H5" target="_blank">Spotify</a>
        <a href="https://music.apple.com/us/album/waiting-for-rover-ep/1822589894" target="_blank">Apple Music</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_lqEcVBijeakOThABs2QHeLU7wPVUiZ3EU" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
        <a href="https://music.amazon.com/albums/B0FF6TZ33Q" target="_blank">Amazon</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BIO SECTION -->
    <section id="about">
      <h2>What are we?</h2>
          <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">
               Death Ponee is an electronic post-punk band from Prague, built on live synths, searing guitars, uptempo drums — and no sequencers. It started with me, a cellist-turned-synth player, writing moody tracks on a digital piano and wanting to build something raw and live. I called up people I’d played with before, picked up a synth, and we got to work.
          </p>
          <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 1.5rem auto 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">
               Our first album (Life's Great Uniform) was instrumental. Waiting for Rover is the first time I sing. We’re now a four-piece: two synths, guitar, drums, and a tiny 8-bit sampler called the MicroGranny making weird noises at the edge of everything.
          </p>
 
    </section>

  </body>
</html>
